C) QA & Balance Guardrails (reference)

Duels (same tier): 8–14 s TTK target bands.

Energy sustain: baseline builds ≥8–10 s of continuous fire + maneuver; Advanced +15–25%.

Mobility ladder: Strike > Escort > Line > Capital.

Sensors ladder: Larger hulls trend to higher DRADIS; Visual rises modestly.

FTL: Bigger hulls → longer Range and higher Cost; Command frames may have transponder discounts.

Slot identity: Enforce role signatures (Interceptor=Engine, Assault=Hull, Command=Computer) on base & Advanced.
